		id

		externalId

		accountUsername
		displayName
		frontEnvironment
		frontVersion
		backEnvironment
		backVersion
		subject
		description
		attachments
		screenRecording
		meta
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

query ($query:QueryStatement)
{
	supportFindIssue (query: $query)
	{
		id

		externalId

		externalColorStatus

		displayName
		frontEnvironment
		frontVersion
		backEnvironment
		backVersion

		description
		attachments

		meta
		createdAt
		updatedAt

}

}
